Updated [density_main.cpp](/home/khkramer/src/nemotron-january-2026/proj-2026-05-24-from-scratch-runtime/runtime/cpp/density_main.cpp:157) with `NEMOTRON_DENSITY_BATCH_STEADY` default-off flag parsing and [a `--mode b1-t1` gate](/home/khkramer/src/nemotron-january-2026/proj-2026-05-24-from-scratch-runtime/runtime/cpp/density_main.cpp:2146). Pad policy is duplicate row 0 into unused bucket rows; pads are discarded on unpack.

